metadata.name: Moon Flower
metadata.description:
As an artist, I have always been drawn to the beauty of nature and the intricacies of the divine feminine. My latest artwork, "Moon Flower," is a tribute to both of these timeless themes, brought to life with the help of artificial intelligence. 

Inspired by the stunning lighting design in the show "Euphoria," and my portrait photography I set out to capture the ethereal glow of the moon and the dreamlike quality of the feminine spirit. Through countless hours of experimentation and refinement, I trained my AI to create images that were both beautiful and deeply emotional.

The result is a series of images that celebrate the power and grace of women, while also paying homage to the sublime majesty of the natural world. Through "Moon Flower," I hope to inspire others to explore their own creativity and connect with the world around them in new and meaningful ways. 

Artist Statement was written in collaboration with ChatGPT 

Art is an AI collaborative piece created with Midjourney
